snippet.title: League Of Enthusiastic Losers - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
League Of Enthusiastic Losers on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1388650/League_Of_Enthusiastic_Losers

League of Enthusiastic Losers is an adventure game about caring for yourself and your friends, and about not having to be unhappy, just because you are a loser in the eyes of others.

Source: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qp81-LlFDc0
